that's one of the central responsibilities

00:18:19.930 --> 00:18:22.210
of the Justice Department, and so for them

00:18:22.210 --> 00:18:24.860
to support a constitutional exemption

00:18:24.860 --> 00:18:27.410
to non-discrimination law is remarkable,

00:18:27.410 --> 00:18:30.100
