and are opposing us.

00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:25.530
We are, we're suing
over your privacy rights

00:19:25.530 --> 00:19:29.630
with respect to the cell,
the data on your cellphone,

00:19:29.630 --> 00:19:32.360
and the Trump administration's
arguing it should be able

00:19:32.360 --> 00:19:34.110
to get the data on your cellphone,

00:19:34.110 --> 00:19:37.780
as to where you, where
