And we saw it, you know,

00:28:11.878 --> 00:28:16.878
the day after the
president was inaugurated,

00:28:17.060 --> 00:28:20.160
with the women's march,
and just a remarkable,

00:28:20.160 --> 00:28:23.200
nation-wide, world-wide uprising

00:28:24.748 --> 00:28:29.540
of people who came together
to stand up against

00:28:29.540 --> 00:28:34.540
what this newly inaugurated
president stood for.

